  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is conducted in Asia. The aim of this observational study is, under normal
      clinical practice conditions, to investigate the clinical safety and effectiveness in Chinese
      patients with type 2 diabetes who have never received anti-diabetic treatment before.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
